    "These include the automated test case generation of various scenarios such as enhancing the coverage of testing [129,157] and the detection of possible defects [157].",
    "Ryan et al. [124] proposes to provide LLMs with path constrains and code context to improve the coverage of generated test cases.",
    "ChatUniTest [157] extracts essential information and creates an adaptive focal context for LLMs to generate test cases.",
    "PROGRAM REPAIR AND AUTO-CODINGProgram synthesis converts a formal or semi-formal specification into expressions or code snippets.",
